{"tid":1945983,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】支那公安互毆：湖北黃梅交警VS江西九江特警","createTime":"2020-03-27T11:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T16:06:43.000Z","uid":49136,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b237130b4d085987780d8b69295025eb78b80476","tid":1945983,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T11:17:48.000Z","msg":"事情起因據說是湖北黃梅縣打開關卡之後，交界的江西九江市跑到湖北境內的長江大橋一頭設卡禁止湖北人入內。黃梅縣交警與九江的警察理論，結果一個人被九江10幾個警察圍毆，引發橋上民眾不滿，出現了警車被打翻的高雅畫面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tns4Dsr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftns4Dsr.jpg&h=2905fbd5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EMuKDss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEMuKDss.jpg&h=5f257a67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影片合集（幾十個影片，順序好像有點亂。請大家慢慢觀看）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/16g-KyRPhLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F16g-KyRPhLQ&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=953fa7ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/16g-KyRPhLQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0S6FQl2hsKM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0S6FQl2hsKM&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=6744f3ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0S6FQl2hsKM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XW4v8jV-7hA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXW4v8jV-7hA&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=130261fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XW4v8jV-7hA</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Elizabeth1989zz/status/1243452726027137024\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FElizabeth1989zz%2Fstatus%2F1243452726027137024&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=dd7cc5d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FElizabeth1989zz%2Fstatus%2F1243452726027137024&h=c51bce89\" data-